{"tid":1500961,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"有市民到港台抗議 有人向記者揮拳 指罵記者為「垃圾」","createTime":"2019-08-24T08:05:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T14:04:34.000Z","uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1e2044f98262ca6d89fd93fbb171d182209321e7","tid":1500961,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T08:05:55.000Z","msg":"香港政研會發起「萬人包圍香港電台」行動，大批市民在港台廣播大廈外聚集，企滿正門對出兩邊行人路，部分人企出馬路。不少人情緒激動，向記者高叫「黑記」、「暴徒」，又拍攝記者樣貌，甚至有推撞。有示威者向一名攝影記者揮拳，這名攝影記者報稱頭部被打中。<br />\n<br />\n有人對身穿黑色上衣的記者說，著上黑衣已是有立場；有人指罵記者為「垃圾」。<br />\n<br />\n另外，有不少人在廣播大廈外綁上綠絲帶，又貼上標語及海報，部分寫上「港台亂港」。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1476508-20190824.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1476508-20190824.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=LRWPp57H9HH2b7ruXTkGLrTKTGNgLIIXgyzGYx6bzTs%3D&h=4ea2e693\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1476508-20190824.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=f6cec84e\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1476508-20190824.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"aa0a44674f842d147f0ae662bbd7253fed3e7dd8","tid":1500961,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T14:04:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}